  <brief_title>A Preoperative Cognitive Behavioural Therapy Program Based on Self-determination Theory for Bariatric Surgery Candidates</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACRoBAT</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a Preoperative Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT) Program Based on Self-determination Theory for Bariatric Surgery Candidates : an Open-label Controlled, Randomized, Superiority Study</official_title>
