  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to evaluate the impact of a pre-surgical intervention program
      based on Cognitive and Behavioural Emotional Therapies, on the degree of dietary restriction
      of patients who are candidates for bariatric surgery in order to increase the long-term
      effectiveness of this kind of surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
