      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient starting a preparation for bariatric surgery in the endocrinology department
             at St Philibert Hospital

          -  18 ≤Age≤60 years

          -  Patient meeting the criteria of the High Authority of Health (HAS) for the agreement
